    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a reliable companion. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved, meaning it\u2019s got that perfect balance of being dependable and ready for many more miles. It runs like a dream and is just waiting for someone new to take it on its next adventure! If you're looking for a great, honest car that won't let you down, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
