    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound 2008 Chevrolet Corvette Z06, a masterclass in naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart lies the 7.0L LS7 V8, featuring a dry-sump lubrication system, titanium connecting rods, and CNC-ported cylinder heads capable of a 7,000 RPM redline. Power is managed via a Tremec TR-6060 6-speed manual transaxle and a limited-slip differential. This Z06 utilizes a lightweight hydroformed aluminum chassis and magnesium engine cradle to minimize unsprung weight and maximize structural rigidity. The braking system consists of 6-piston front and 4-piston rear monoblock calipers over cross-drilled rotors. Meticulously maintained, the valvetrain and cooling systems are in excellent operational order. This vehicle represents a pure, analog driving experience for the discerning performance enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
