      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a distinguished example of automotive engineering, maintained to an exemplary standard. This vehicle offers a harmonious balance of performance and reliability, featuring a well-preserved interior and a robust mechanical profile. Having undergone a comprehensive inspection to ensure its structural and operational integrity, it stands ready to deliver a premium driving experience. We invite serious inquiries to appreciate the refined character and enduring quality of this exceptional offering.",
