    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my car, and it\u2019s honestly such a solid ride. It\u2019s been super reliable for me and is in really nice shape, perfect for someone who wants a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. It drives smoothly and has been well-loved! I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I\u2019m excited for someone else to get some great miles out of it. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come check it out!",
      "price": 29900.0,
