    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust BMW E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 inline-six engine. This unit has been meticulously maintained with a recent VANOS overhaul and comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement already completed\u2014essential for this chassis. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission shifts with precision, aided by a refreshed clutch assembly. Suspension has been upgraded to Bilstein dampers for improved lateral stability without compromising street compliance. The limited-slip differential remains tight, providing excellent torque distribution. While the finish shows minor road wear consistent with enthusiast use, the powertrain is optimized for high-revving performance. Ready for immediate spirited driving.",
